data.description:
This spacious Valero model offers a desirable split floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by soaring 12-foot ceilings and gorgeous hardwood flooring. The large family room features a cozy gas fireplace and extensive built-in shelving. The kitchen opens seamlessly to the family room, making it ideal for entertaining guests.
This home features hard maple cabinets throughout, including matching custom built-in shelving and desk areas in the kitchen and office/den, which offer convenient workspaces for remote work or studying.  The kitchen and attached butler's pantry offer plentiful storage and counter space. 
The generous backyard is perfect for entertaining, with an extended patio, built-in BBQ, and synthetic putting green.  The East-facing exposure ensures bright, sunny mornings and cool, shaded evenings. 
The large master bedroom features a separate tub and glass block shower, double vanity sinks, and a roomy walk-in closet.
Parking will never be an issue, with separate single and two-car garages and ample driveway space.  Both garages have durable, epoxy-coated floors. 
The owner has recently installed energy-efficient upgrades including newer A/C units and low-E windows, which keep cooling costs down in summer months. 
Nestled on a quiet street near the gate-guarded entrance to the country club, this home is conveniently located near great schools, shopping centers, dining options, and easy highway access.  Living within this award-winning community, you'll have year-round access to two championship golf courses, each with private clubhouses, restaurants, fitness centers and tennis/pickleball courts. 
Don't miss the chance to make this beautiful home your own! Owner/Agent will respond promptly to all inquiries and is prepared to close quickly. See this one today and experience the charm and elegance of Anthem Golf & Country Club!
